<!DOCTYPE HTML><html><head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Edward Professional Advisors - Consulting</title><link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.ico" /><meta name="description" content="Write description here."><meta name="keywords" content="insert, keywords, here"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"><link rel="stylesheet" href="consulting.css" type="text/css" media="screen"><link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:400,700" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"></head><body><div class="container"><div id="header"><div id="i1"><a href="index.php"><img src="images/banner.gif" style="width: 100%; height: auto;"></a></div></div><div id="i2"><div id="i3"><div class="page-title">Consulting</div><div id="i5"><div class="h2"><b>What is Organizational Consulting?</b></div><div id="i7"><div><b>Organizational consulting</b> is using knowledge and experience to solve organizational challenges. Most organizational leaders don’t have the time or resources to keep abreast of the latest research findings or emerging best practices in their industries. Edward</div><span style="background-color: inherit;">Professional Advisors has an extensive network of researchers and practitioners who are experienced at delivering sustainable results.</span> </div></div><div class="hr"></div><div id="i9"><div class="h2"><b>What Can I Expect From a Consulting Engagement?</b><br></div><div id="i11"><div>Our consulting engagements occur in five distinct and dynamic phases:</div><div><ol><li><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;"><b>Investigation.</b> We learn about the client and the challenge the client wants to resolve.</span><br></li><li><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;"><b>Planning.</b> We work with the client to create an effective action plan.</span><br></li><li><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;"><b>Implementation.</b> We perform the consulting </span><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;">intervention.</span></li><li><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;"><b>Evaluation.</b> We evaluate the success of the consulting intervention.</span><br></li><li><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;"><b>Follow-Up.</b> We work with the client to make further changes to the consulting intervention or organization.</span><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;"> </span><br></li></ol></div></div></div><div class="hr"></div><div id="i13"><div class="h2"><b>Why Are An Increasing Number of Organizations Hiring Organizational Consultants?</b><br></div><div id="i15"><div><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;">The simple answer is because organizational consultants add value to organizations. Organizational leaders hire Edward Professional Advisors because we increase profits, raise morale, improve productivity, increase customer satisfaction, and deliver the solutions that improve our clients’ organizations.</span><br></div></div></div><div class="next-page"><div id="i17"><a href="industrial-organizational-psych.php"><u>Next: Industrial-Organizational Psychology &gt;</u></a></div></div><div class="prev-page"><div id="i19"><a href="latin-america.php"><u>&lt; Previous: Doing Business in Latin America</u></a></div></div><div style="clear: both;"></div></div></div><div id="footer"><div id="i21">© 2016 - EDWARD PROFESSIONAL ADVISORS<div>info@edwardpa.com</div><div>888-858-9510<br></div></div></div></div></body></html>